high_descs: Turn left, then turn left again, then turn right to go to the counter next to the sink.
Pick up the left most spray bottle from the counter.
Turn around, then go right to go to the toilet.
Put the spray bottle on the back of the toilet, toward the center.
Return to the counter, next to the sink.
Pick up the spray bottle, on top of the counter.
Turn around and return to the toilet.
Place the spray bottle on the back of the toilet, next to the other spray bottle.
anns.task_desc: Put the spray bottles on the back of the toilet.

high_descs: Turn around to the left and walk over to the white stand beside the tub.
Pick up the cleaning bottle closest to the edge of the stand top.
Turn around to the right and walk to the toilet.
Place the cleaner bottle on the toilet tank.
Back away from the toilet, turn to the left, and walk back to the white stand.
Pick up the remaining cleaner bottle.
Turn around to the right and walk back to the toilet.
Place the cleaner bottle onto the toilet tank.
anns.task_desc: Moving cleaner bottles from a bathroom stand to the toilet tank.

high_descs: turn left and walk over to the cabinet at the end of the room on the left
grab a spray bottle off of the cabinet
turn around and walk over to the right side of the toilet at the end of the room
place the spray bottle down on top of the toilet
turn left and walk over to the cabinet at the end of the room again on the left
grab the spray bottle off of the cabinet
turn around and walk back over to the toilet at the end of the room
place the spray bottle down on top of the toilet next to the other spray bottle
anns.task_desc: place two spray bottles down on top of the toilet

high_descs: Turn around and walk straight then face the right at the small white counter
Pick up the yellow spray bottle on the left
Turn around and walk straight to the side of the toilet
Place the bottle on the top toilet lid
Turn around and walk straight then face the small white counter
Pick up the yellow spray bottle from the counter
Turn around and walk straight to the side of the toilet
Place the bottle on the top toilet lid
anns.task_desc: Put the spray bottles on the toilet lid

high_descs: Turn around, walk across the room and face the toilet to the right.
Pick up the yellow bottle of spray cleaner on the right on shelving to the right of the sink.
Walk to face the toilet in the opposite corner of the room.
Put the yellow bottle of spray cleaner on the back of the toilet.
Walk to the opposite corner of the room to face the shelving on the right side of the sink.
Pick up the yellow bottle of spray cleaner remaining on the shelving to the right of the sink.
Walk to face the toilet in the opposite corner of the room.
Put the yellow bottle of spray cleaner on the back of the toilet.
anns.task_desc: To move two yellow bottles of spray from a shelf to the back of the toilet.
